#  Functional Requirements — User Stories

## Customer User Stories

### US-01 — User Registration
As a customer, I want to create an account so that I can rent or buy cars using the system.

### US-02 — User Login
As a customer, I want to log in securely so that I can access my bookings and purchases.

### US-03 — Language Selection
As a customer, I want to choose Amharic or English so that I can use the system in my preferred language.

### US-04 — Browse Rental Cars
As a customer, I want to view available rental cars so that I can choose a suitable vehicle.

### US-05 — Search & Filter Rental Cars
As a customer, I want to search and filter rental cars by price, type, and availability so that I can quickly find what I need.

### US-06 — Choose Driving Option
As a customer, I want to select self-drive or with-driver so that I can rent according to my preference.

### US-07 — Select Pickup & Drop-off Location
As a customer, I want to select pickup and drop-off locations using a map so that locations are accurate.

### US-08 — Check Vehicle Availability
As a customer, I want the system to check car availability for my selected dates so that I don’t book an unavailable car.

### US-09 — Create Rental Booking
As a customer, I want to confirm a rental booking so that the car is reserved for me.

### US-10 — Make Rental Payment
As a customer, I want to pay using bank mobile banking so that I can complete my booking.

### US-11 — Submit Payment Reference
As a customer, I want to submit my transaction reference so that my payment can be verified.

### US-12 — Browse Cars for Sale
As a customer, I want to view cars available for sale so that I can decide to buy one.

### US-13 — Search & Filter Cars for Sale
As a customer, I want to filter cars for sale by price and model so that I can find a suitable car.

### US-14 — Purchase a Car
As a customer, I want to purchase a car using mobile banking so that I can buy it online.

### US-15 — View Booking & Purchase History
As a customer, I want to view my rental and purchase history so that I can track my activities.

### US-16 — Cancel Rental Booking
As a customer, I want to cancel a booking so that I can change my plans if needed.

### US-17 — Contact Customer Support
As a customer, I want to contact customer support so that I can get help when I have problems.
